                                <h6>2016-04-28</h6>
                                <p>As Syrian refugees arrive in our country, Canadian reaction is mixed. We all feel the tension between safety, a sense that we have to do something, and a desire to deepen our long-standing reputation as a nation that welcomes immigrants. Many of these reactions are driven by politics, self interest and fear. But how should the Church react?	Let me start by addressing what this has to do with Bible...</p>
