                               	<h3>Hope and Healing - a Refugee Story</h3>
                                <h6>2016-03-29</h6>
                                <p>My name is Rajiya. It means &rsquo;hope&rsquo;. I live in the Middle East, and I am a Christian, a Chaldean Christian. My people have been living in this region for many, many generations, and we are known to some as Assyrian Christians. Our Church holds to a long, venerable tradition.	In the course of the last two years I lost hope. The militant Islamic group known as Da&rsquo;esh or ISIS has been wreaking havoc a...</p>
                                <a class="button" href="blog/post.jsp?euid=3244ef52-e1fa-4324-b">Read More</a>
